resourceInstances.name: compute_1
resourceInstances.description: Represents a real or virtual machine or server. Information specified on the Compute	      node will be used to find the machine that fits the given requirements in the cloud	      available machines. If no sizing information are specified the cloud provider default	      machine will be used. It is strongly recommended to specify the required  CPUs and memory	      at least.
